hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 多方同源性和理想气体定律给出
$$P_c=K_{\rm eff}GM^{2/3}\rho_c^{4/3},\quad P_c=\frac{\rho_c k_BT_c}{\mu m_H}.$$
2. 联立方程并求解 $\rho_c$：
$$\frac{\rho_c k_BT_c}{\mu m_H}=K_{\rm eff}GM^{2/3}\rho_c^{4/3}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\rho_c^{1/3}=\frac{k_BT_c}{\mu m_H\,K_{\rm eff}G\,M^{2/3}}$$
$$\Longrightarrow\;
\rho_c=\Bigl[\frac{k_B}{\mu m_H\,G}\Bigr]^3M^{-2}K_{\rm eff}^{-3}T_c^3.$$
3. 因此 
$$\mathcal A(q_c)=\Bigl[\frac{k_B}{\mu m_H\,G}\Bigr]^3M^{-2}K_{\rm eff}^{-3},$$
其中 
$$K_{\rm eff}=K_{rad}+q_c(K_{conv}-K_{rad})
=K_{rad}\Bigl[1+q_c\frac{K_{conv}-K_{rad}}{K_{rad}}\Bigr].$$
4. 对 $q_c$ 展开至一阶：
$$\mathcal A(q_c)=\Bigl[\frac{k_B}{\mu m_H\,G}\Bigr]^3M^{-2}K_{rad}^{-3}
\Bigl[1+q_c\frac{K_{conv}-K_{rad}}{K_{rad}}\Bigr]^{-3}
\approx\Bigl[\frac{k_B}{\mu m_H\,G}\Bigr]^3M^{-2}K_{rad}^{-3}
\Bigl[1-3q_c\frac{K_{conv}-K_{rad}}{K_{rad}}\Bigr].$$
